publisher			Vladis Fire							
publish_time	 2016年6月17日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Calm farmer life is coming to an end. Fallen warriors of ancient times rose from the dead.Help farmers to fight off raids of evil skeletons and protect their land. The only thing that will separate your territory from the skeletons - the wall. Don't let it fail. You will have bow and quiver of arrows in your starter arsenal. Be precise because one mistake could be your last.Features:• An exciting and intuitive gameplay.• Great minimalistic design.• Divided into waves structure of the game.• Tactical Gameplay: The gameplay will test the strength of your planning skills.• Skilled opponents: you will encounter dangerous enemies such as "bomber" that can transform your wall into a pile of trash.• A variety of weapons: you will get different types of weapons in your hands, such as crossbow and huge cannon.• Help in the fight: you can hire archers and gunners to confront the advancing waves of enemies.						
title	 BoneBone			
